<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1696/71 of 26 July 1971 on the common organization of the market in hops (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1170/77 (2), and in particular Article 7 (5) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 26. juuli 1971. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1696/71 humalaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1170/77, (2) eriti selle artikli 7 l&otilde;iget 5, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Regulation (EEC) No 1170/77 amended the provisions relating to recognized producer groups, particularly in regard to their composition and functions, </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1170/77 on muudetud s&auml;tteid tunnustatud tootjar&uuml;hmade kohta, eriti nende koosseisu ja &uuml;lesannete kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas these functions have been extended; whereas provision should therefore be made that, for a group to be recognized, its rules should include all information necessary for members to be fully aware of their obligations within the group; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuseid &uuml;lesandeid on laiendatud; seet&otilde;ttu tuleks s&auml;testada, et tootjar&uuml;hma tunnustamiseks peaks eeskirjades sisalduma kogu liikmetele vajalik teave nende kohustustest r&uuml;hmas; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1351/72 of 28 June 1972 on the recognition of producer groups for hops (3) should therefore be amended accordingly, in particular as regards the policy of such groups for marketing their production and the administration of the production aid; </inglise>
<eesti> seet&otilde;ttu tuleks vastavalt muuta komisjoni 28. juuni 1972. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1351/72 humalasektori tootjar&uuml;hmade tunnustamise kohta, (3) eelk&otilde;ige niisuguste r&uuml;hmade poliitika osas oma toodangu turustamisel ja tootmistoetuse haldamisel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Hops, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las humalaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
