<inglise> These rules shall comprise at least: (a) as regards production: (aa) The use of one or more specified varieties when renewing plantations or creating new ones, </inglise>
<eesti> Need eeskirjad k&auml;sitlevad v&auml;hemalt: a) tootmise osas: </eesti>
<inglise> (bb) compliance with certain methods of cultivation and plant protection, </inglise>
